 "lines": [
  {
   "i": 1,
   "en": "Ozaki"
  },
  {
   "i": 2,
   "en": "The rookie showdown, at last"
  },
  {
   "i": 3,
   "en": "Eri"
  },
  {
   "i": 4,
   "en": "...Yeah!"
  },
  {
   "i": 5,
   "en": "Okay, let's go"
  },
  {
   "i": 6,
   "en": "...Eri?"
  },
  {
   "i": 7,
   "en": "Those two are waiting"
  },
  {
   "i": 8,
   "en": "Ah, wait, don't run ahead"
  },
  {
   "i": 9,
   "en": "Breathe in... out... in... out..."
  },
  {
   "i": 10,
   "en": "Good. You look great."
  },
  {
   "i": 11,
   "en": "At this rate..."
  },
  {
   "i": 12,
   "en": "Eri? What is it?"
  },
  {
   "i": 13,
   "en": "Hard to believe you agonized so much"
  },
  {
   "i": 14,
   "en": "Have you put it behind you?"
  },
  {
   "i": 15,
   "en": "Yeah"
  },
  {
   "i": 16,
   "en": "I don't know why, but I'm glad"
  },
  {
   "i": 17,
   "en": "Idols outside the net"
  },
  {
   "i": 18,
   "en": "are a little strange..."
  },
  {
   "i": 19,
   "en": "Hm? Strange how?"
  },
  {
   "i": 20,
   "en": "Well... friends turn into rivals..."
  },
  {
   "i": 21,
   "en": "and even after they become rivals,"
  },
  {
   "i": 22,
   "en": "they somehow stay friends"
  },
  {
   "i": 23,
   "en": "Ah, I see what you mean"
  },
  {
   "i": 24,
   "en": "Now that you say it, it's true"
  },
  {
   "i": 25,
   "en": "Drawing close, drifting apart,"
  },
  {
   "i": 26,
   "en": "joining hands, then clashing..."
  },
  {
   "i": 27,
   "en": "The bonds between idols keep"
  },
  {
   "i": 28,
   "en": "changing, in all sorts of ways"
  },
  {
   "i": 29,
   "en": "Huh... so it's all hazy"
  },
  {
   "i": 30,
   "en": "That's right. Hazy"
  },
  {
   "i": 31,
   "en": "But that's... the interesting part?"
  },
  {
   "i": 32,
   "en": "Right. There's not one bond you can"
  },
  {
   "i": 33,
   "en": "count on to never change"
  },
  {
   "i": 34,
   "en": "With a single exception. Eri, the one"
  },
  {
   "i": 35,
   "en": "person who is always on your side..."
  },
  {
   "i": 36,
   "en": "Just you, Ms. Ozaki?"
  },
  {
   "i": 37,
   "en": "Right. Whatever happens, I'm with you"
  },
  {
   "i": 38,
   "en": "You can trust in that"
  },
  {
   "i": 39,
   "en": "Let's win. And from here on out,"
  },
  {
   "i": 40,
   "en": "let's move forward hand in hand"
  },
  {
   "i": 41,
   "en": "Yeah!"
  },
  {
   "i": 42,
   "en": "Just the President?"
  },
  {
   "i": 43,
   "en": "Even she won't go that far for you"
  },
  {
   "i": 44,
   "en": "Running a business means being"
  },
  {
   "i": 45,
   "en": "coldly practical at times"
  },
  {
   "i": 46,
   "en": "Then... she isn't completely"
  },
  {
   "i": 47,
   "en": "on my side either"
  },
  {
   "i": 48,
   "en": "Right. But don't worry. ―㌍I'm here"
  },
  {
   "i": 49,
   "en": "You are?"
  },
  {
   "i": 50,
   "en": "Just myself?"
  },
  {
   "i": 51,
   "en": "True. You'll never betray yourself."
  },
  {
   "i": 52,
   "en": "But..."
  },
  {
   "i": 53,
   "en": "isn't putting it that way"
  },
  {
   "i": 54,
   "en": "a little cold?"
  },
  {
   "i": 55,
   "en": "You have one more ally, don't you?"
  },
  {
   "i": 56,
   "en": "One more..."
  },
  {
   "i": 57,
   "en": "...Oh!"
  },
  {
   "i": 58,
   "en": "Figured it out?"
  },
  {
   "i": 59,
   "en": "...Who?"
  },
  {
   "i": 60,
   "en": "Honestly... It's me! Me!"
  },
  {
   "i": 61,
   "en": "You, Ms. Ozaki?"
  },
  {
   "i": 62,
   "en": "Yes. No matter what happens, I'll"
  },
  {
   "i": 63,
   "en": "always be right here supporting you"
  },
  {
   "i": 64,
   "en": "So go fight without fear"
  },
  {
   "i": 65,
   "en": "...Okay"
  },
  {
   "i": 66,
   "en": "Ai-chan and Ryo-san told me before:"
  },
  {
   "i": 67,
   "en": "'Win or lose, we're all still friends'"
  },
  {
   "i": 68,
   "en": "I'll give it my all. That's surely..."
  },
  {
   "i": 69,
   "en": "for my sake, and for everyone's!"
  }
 ]
